RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LBTMS_STP_PRODUCT_MAPPING.LS_BRANCH=LBTMS_STP_COMPONENT_MAPPING.LS_BRANCH AND LBTMS_STP_PRODUCT_MAPPING.LS_PRODUCT=LBTMS_STP_COMPONENT_MAPPING.LS_PRODUCT AND LBTMS_STP_PRODUCT_MAPPING.SELF_PARTICIPANT=LBTMS_STP_COMPONENT_MAPPING.SELF_PARTICIPANT AND LBTMS_STP_PRODUCT_MAPPING.LS_CCY=LBTMS_STP_COMPONENT_MAPPING.LS_CCY AND LBTMS_STP_PRODUCT_MAPPING.LD_BRANCH = LBTMS_STP_COMPONENT_MAPPING.LD_BRANCH AND LBTMS_STP_PRODUCT_MAPPING.LD_PRODUCT = LBTMS_STP_COMPONENT_MAPPING.LD_PRODUCT AND LBTMS_STP_PRODUCT_MAPPING.TRADE_STANDARD= LBTMS_STP_COMPONENT_MAPPING.TRADE_STANDARD

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT BRANCH_CODE,BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTM_BRANCH WHERE AUTH_STAT='A' AND RECORD_STAT='O' UNION ALL SELECT 'ALL','ALL' FROM DUAL

SELECT A.PRODUCT_CODE,A.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT A,OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT AND A.MODULE = 'OL' /*AND B.AGENCY_CONTRACT = 'Y' */ AND B.PRODUCT_TYPE = (SELECT C.PRODUCT_TYPE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD C WHERE C.PRODUCT = ?) AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND ((? = 'M' AND NVL(B.LMA_PARTICIPATION,'N') = 'Y' AND B.PRODUCT_TYPE='L') OR (? <> 'M' AND NVL(B.LMA_PARTICIPATION,'N') = 'N' AND B.PRODUCT_TYPE='L')OR B.PRODUCT_TYPE<>'L')

SELECT PORTFOLIO,BRANCH,DESK_CODE, /*EXPENSE_CODE,*/ CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM TLTMS_PORTFOLIO A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.PORTFOLIO = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' UNION SELECT 'ALL', 'ALL', 'ALL', 'ALL' /*,'ALL'*/ FROM DUAL
SELECT PRODUCT_CODE, PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT where module = 'LB' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A'AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' UNION SELECT '*.*', 'ALL CURRENCIES' FROM DUAL
SELECT TREASURY_SOURCE,SOURCE_DESCRIPTION,TREASURY_GROUP FROM OLTM_TREASURY_SOURCE WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT DISTINCT (Component), Component_Description FROM Lftms_Product_Iccf WHERE Product = ? AND Nvl(Unfund_Component, 'N') = 'N' UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT (Component), Description FROM Lftms_Product_Fee WHERE Product_Code = ? UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT (Af.Component), Afd.Class_Description Description FROM Lftms_Product_Accr_Fee Af, Oltm_Class Afd WHERE Product_Code = ? AND Af.Component = Afd.Class_Code AND Afd.Module = 'LB' UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT (Rule) component, NULL Description FROM txtm_product_tax WHERE Product = ?

SELECT DISTINCT (Component), Component_Description FROM Lftms_Product_Iccf WHERE Product = ? AND Nvl(Unfund_Component, 'N') = 'N' UNION ALL SELECT Component, Description FROM Lftms_Product_Fee WHERE Basis_Amount_Tag = 'USERINPUT' AND Product_Code = ? UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT (Af.Component), Afd.Class_Description Description FROM Lftms_Product_Accr_Fee Af, Oltm_Class Afd WHERE Product_Code = ? AND Af.Component = Afd.Class_Code AND Afd.Module = 'OL' UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT (Rule) component, NULL Description FROM txtm_product_tax WHERE Product = ?
